description:
Quick, make a wish... 

What did you wish for? Look closer because this is not your ordinary backyard dandelion. These flying teal pods are ready to transport your wind powered wishes off into the sunset.

Wrap it up and share a wish with a friend or frame it and keep your wishes all to yourself. 

//Limited edition art print. 2nd ed. 39 total in this edition.

//Size is 7.5"x10" 

//Printed on 100% cotton 110# Crane Lettra flourescent white stock. 

// Each card has been hand-fed and printed on a vintage Golding Pearl letterpress. Because of the nature of this process, no two prints will be exactly alike.

